revision.text:
'''Munakata Shrine''' (宗像神社, Munakata Jinja) is a shrine dedicated to the Munakata Three Goddesses (宗像三女神), who are deities of the sea and navigation. The shrine is also referred to as '''Munakata Shrine''' (宗形神社), '''Munekata Shrine''' (胸形神社), and '''Munakata Shrine''' (胸肩神社), among other variations.
== Overview ==
The {{ill|Munakata Three Goddesses|ja|宗像三女神|lt=Munakata Three Goddesses|12=draft|12=draft}}—{{ill|Tagorihime|ja|田心姫神|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tagitsuhime|ja|湍津姫神|12=draft|12=draft}}, and {{ill|Ichikishimahime|ja|市杵島姫神|12=draft|12=draft}}—are enshrined as the main deities. Shrines bearing the name "Munakata Shrine" are found across Japan, with the head shrine being {{ill|Munakata Taisha|ja|宗像大社|12=draft|12=draft}} in Munakata City, Fukuoka Prefecture.
Munakata Shrines are primarily dedicated to ensuring safe navigation and are concentrated along coastal areas of the Seto Inland Sea and the Kansai region. In the Kanto region, a cluster of Munakata Shrines can be found around {{ill|Inbanuma|ja|印旛沼|12=draft|12=draft}}. Notably, Munakata-lineage shrines rank fifth in number nationwide.
== Major Munakata Shrines Nationwide ==
=== Head Shrine ===
*
* {{ill|Munakata Shrine (Hirosaki)|ja|胸肩神社 (青森県弘前市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Hirosaki City)
* * {{ill|Munekata Shrine (Oyama)|ja|胸形神社 (小山市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Oyama City) *
*
* {{ill|Munakata Shrine (Shiroi)|ja|宗像神社 (白井市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Shiroi City) * {{ill|Amanomiya Shrine|ja|天宮神社|1=Ame-no-Miya Shrine|12=draft|12=draft}} (Morimachi, Shuchi District)
* {{ill|Munakata Shrine (Kyoto)|ja|宗像神社 (京都市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Kyoto Gyoen, Kyoto City) * {{ill|Ichitanidani Munakata Shrine|ja|櫟谷宗像神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Arashiyama, Kyoto City) * {{ill|Munakata Shrine (Sakurai)|ja|宗像神社 (桜井市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Toyama, Sakurai City)
* {{ill|Munakata Shrine (Kita-ku, Okayama)|ja|宗形神社 (岡山市北区)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Kita-ku, Okayama City) == See Also == * {{ill|Munakata Taisha|ja|宗像大社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Itsukushima Shrine (disambiguation)|ja|厳島神社 (曖昧さ回避)|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Ichikishima Shrine|ja|市杵島神社|12=draft|12=draft}}
